  "description": "Bulk primary forming at the smelter and mill: continuous casting (strand solidification from molten steel), hot rolling (slab/billet to sheet/plate/structural), extrusion (aluminum profiles), wire rod rolling, forging at scale (open-die hydraulic press, closed-die), and structural section rolling (I-beams, rails). Transforms raw metal into stock shapes for downstream manufacturing.",
